Henry Kravis - Wikipedia





















 






Henry Kravis

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Henry Kravis



Kravis in 2016



Born
(1944-01-06) January 6, 1944 (age 73)
Tulsa, Oklahoma, U.S.


Residence
New York, New York, U.S.
Palm Beach, Florida, U.S.
Meeker, Colorado, U.S.


