Interesting Facts
KKR & Co. owns a 2006 Challenger 604 business jet purchased in 2006 serial number 5637 registration number N637TF (expired in January 31, 2015); a 2001 Bombardier Global Express jet purchased in 2001 serial number 9039 registration number N90EW (expires in March 31, 2017); and a 2001 Hawker 800XP purchased in 2013 serial number 258648 registration number N483AM (expired in January 31, 2016). The jets are owned through EAC Air, EWA West and ABME Aviation respectively.
